OL,3,CParents of stabbed teenager 'begged'
OL,4,Cpolice to send him to prison, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe parents of a teenager stabbed to
OL,8,Fdeath have told a court of their
OL,9,Fefforts to save him from his drug
OL,10,Fdealing and debts.
OL,12,FMustafa Momand racked up a shared
OL,13,F#20,000 drug debt and was knifed in
OL,14,Fbroad daylight in central Brighton on
OL,15,FOctober 5 2023.
OL,17,FBefore his death, his mother Suraya
OL,18,FMomand said he told her he "regretted
OL,19,Feverything" and talked about going to
OL,20,Fcollege to study law to help exploited
OL,21,Fchildren.
