OL,3,CParents of stabbed teenager 'begged'
OL,4,Cpolice to send him to prison, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FJurors heard how Mustafa had moved to
OL,8,Fthe UK from Afghanistan with his
OL,9,Ffamily in 2009 when he was three years
OL,10,Fold, and in late 2021 his mother found
OL,11,Fcannabis in his room and suspected he
OL,12,Fwas using or dealing drugs.
OL,14,FIn a statement read aloud to court on
OL,15,FTuesday, Mustafa's father, Noor
OL,16,FMomand, said he first became worried
OL,17,Fwhen his son came home very late on
OL,18,Fhis 16th birthday despite his family
OL,19,Fwaiting with a birthday cake for him.
