OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMrs Momand said in a statement read
OL,8,Faloud to court that he argued with
OL,9,Fher, his father and siblings and that
OL,10,Fhe was going more against them and
OL,11,Fseparate from the family.
OL,13,FOn one occasion she said Mustafa went
OL,14,Fmissing for three days because he was
OL,15,Fangry with her for speaking to the
OL,16,Fpolice about him.
OL,18,FShe said: "I was just a very worried
OL,19,Fmother. I was scared for his safety, I
OL,20,Ffelt like I was losing my son."
