OL,7,FShe described how Mustafa told her he
OL,8,Fwanted to stop dealing in future, and
OL,9,Fsaid a man who gives him the drugs
OL,10,F"favours" him.
OL,12,FBur he added that he was in debt to
OL,13,Fthe man because of losing drugs and
OL,14,Fmoney when he gets arrested by police.
OL,16,F"Mustafa took me aside one day and
OL,17,Fasked if we could stop fighting and he
OL,18,Fcould have his mum back," she said.
