OL,7,FMrs Momand said he told her he had
OL,8,Fstarted attending mosque, playing
OL,9,Ffootball and had made nice friends
OL,10,Fsince his move.
OL,12,FMr Momand added while Mustafa was in
OL,13,Fcare: "He was showing he was sorry and
OL,14,Fbeing kind and nice to me and my
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,F"He didn't go out a lot, he said he
OL,18,Fwanted to get away from these people."
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
